paths.summary: Get the OData MockData details corresponding to the ID

name: CoreAPI Connectivity_ODataMockData
about:
Description

Mocking of data is essentially simulating the behaviour of real data in controlled ways. 

Planet 9 Connectivity_oDataMockData essentially simulating the behaviour of real data in controlled ways. When developing an application with oData backend, it is handy to have some mock data available. Some of time backend data is not ready than the developer can use mock data to run the application.

API Connectivity_oDataMockData can used in your app if you want to get an oData MockData list, selected oData MockData details, delete the existing oData MockData or add the new MockData.

Every app must have the right roles (permissions) that enables to access the Planet9 oDataMockData.

Operations Performed 

List

Get the oData MockData list

ResponseList(array) - Definition

Get

Get the oData MockData details related to the Id

RequestID
ResponseList(object) - Definition     

Delete

Delete the oData MockData
